ng-head\">\n              <h1> 可编程组态开发软件 </h1>\n            </div>\n            <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n              <li>文档丰富/界面人性化</li>\n              <li>组态开发周期短</li>\n              <li>组态程序运行稳定</li>\n              <li>多媒体影音支持</li>\n              <li>机器视觉识别处理</li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-3 col-sm-3\">\n          <div class=\"pricing-table wow fadeInUp\">\n            <div class=\"pricing-head\">\n              <h1> 跨平台行业应用程序 </h1>\n            </div>\n            <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n              <li>原生HMI设备运行</li>\n              <li>Android平台运行</li>\n              <li>Windows平台运行</li>\n              <li>定制系统运行</li>\n              <li>原生Android系统</li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-3 col-sm-3\">\n          <div class=\"pricing-table wow fadeInUp\">\n            <div class=\"pricing-head\">\n              <h1> 物联网平台数据扩展 </h1>\n            </div>\n            <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n              <li>多设备集中监控</li>\n              <li>云平台服务接口</li>\n              <li>大数据挖掘分析</li>\n              <li>资源远程上下载</li>\n              <li>可接入ERP/MES</li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-3 col-sm-3\">\n          <div class=\"pricing-table wow fadeInUp\">\n            <div class=\"pricing-head\">\n              <h1> 多样化二次开发接口 </h1>\n            </div>\n            <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n              <li>Linux/Android二次开发</li>\n              <li>Windows兼容开发</li>\n              <li>定制图形UI界面</li>\n              <li>硬件功能可扩展</li>\n              <li>设备外观可定制</li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <!--price end-->\n      </div>\n      <!-- /row -->\n\n    </div>\n    <!-- /container -->\n\n  </div>\n  <!-- service end -->\n\n  <div class=\"container\">\n\n    <div class=\"row mar-b-60\">\n      <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n        <!--tab start-->\n        <section class=\"tab wow fadeInLeft\">\n          <header class=\"panel-heading tab-bg-dark-navy-blue\">\n            <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs nav-justified \">\n              <li class=\"active\">\n                <a data-toggle=\"tab\" href=\"#news\">新闻动态</a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a data-toggle=\"tab\" href=\"#events\">资料下载</a>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"\">\n                <a data-toggle=\"tab\" href=\"#notice-board\">培训教程</a>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"panel-body\">\n            <div class=\"tab-content tasi-tab\">\n              <div id=\"news\" class=\"tab-pane fade in active\">\n                <@cms_content catalogalias=\"news\" level=\"CurrentAndChild\" size=\"3\">\n                  <#list DataList as content>\n                    <article class=\"media\">\n                      <div class=\"media-body b-btm\">\n                        <a href=\"${content.link}\" class=\" p-head\">${content.title}</a>\n                        <p>${content.subTitle!}</p>\n                      </div>\n                    </article>\n                  </#list>\n                </@cms_content>\n              </div>\n              <div id=\"events\" class=\"tab-pane fade\">\n                <@cms_content catalogalias=\"download\" level=\"CurrentAndChild\" size=\"3\">\n                  <#list DataList as content>\n                    <article class=\"media\">\n                      <div class=\"media-body b-btm\">\n                        <a href=\"${content.link}\" class=\" p-head\">${content.title}</a>\n                        <p>${content.subTitle!}</p>\n                      </div>\n                    </article>\n                  </#list>\n                </@cms_content>\n              </div>\n              <div id=\"notice-board\" class=\"tab-pane fade\">\n                <@cms_content catalogalias=\"tutorial\" level=\"CurrentAndChild\" size=\"3\">\n                  <#list DataList as content>\n                    <article class=\"media\">\n                      <div class=\"media-body b-btm\">\n                        <a href=\"${content.link}\" class=\" p-head\">${content.title}</a>\n                        <p>${content.subTitle!}</p>\n                      </div>\n                    </article>\n                  </#list>\n                  </z:list>\n                </@cms_content>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n        <!--tab end-->\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n        <!--testimonial start-->\n        <div class=\"about-testimonial boxed-style about-flexslider \">\n          <section class=\"slider wow fadeInRight\">\n            <div class=\"flexslider\">\n              <ul class=\"slides about-flex-slides\">\n                <@cms_content catalogalias=\"feedback\" size=\"5\">\n                  <#list DataList as content>\n                    <li>\n                      <#if content.logo??>\n                        <div class=\"about-testimonial-image \">\n                          <img alt=\"\" src=\"${content.logo}\" style=\"width:100px;height:100px;\">\n                        </div>\n                      </#if>\n                      <a class=\"about-testimonial-author\" href=\"#\">${content.title}</a>\n                      <span class=\"about-testimonial-company\">${content.subTitle!}</span>\n                      <div class=\"about-testimonial-content\">\n                        <p class=\"about-testimonial-quote\">${content.summary!}</p>\n                      </div>\n                    </li>\n                  </#list>\n                </@cms_content>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </section>\n        </div>\n        <!--testimonial end-->\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n\n  <!--recent work start-->\n  <div class=\"bg-lg\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-12 recent\">\n          <h3 class=\"recent-work\">应用领域</h3>\n          <p>APPLICATION CATEGORY</p>\n          <div id=\"owl-demo\" class=\"owl-carousel owl-theme wow fadeIn\">\n            <@cms_content catalogalias=\"case\" size=\"10\">\n              <#list DataList as content>\n                <div class=\"item view view-tenth\">\n                  <#if content.logo??>\n                  <img src=\"${imageSize(content.logo,280,280)}\" alt=\"${content.title}\">\n                  </#if>\n                  <div class=\"mask\">\n                    <a href=\"${content.link}\" class=\"info\" data-toggle=\"tooltip\" data-placement=\"top\" title=\"Details\">\n                      ${content.title}\n                    </a>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </#list>\n            </@cms_content>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--recent work end-->\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"hr\">\n    <span class=\"hr-inner\"></span>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"row mar-b-50 our-clients\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-3\">\n        <h2>合作共赢</h2>\n        <p>思威控自动化解决方案专家，为客户提高生产效率和生产价值是我们的宗旨！</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col-md-9\">\n        <div class=\"outside\">\n          <p>\n            <span id=\"slider-prev\">\n            </span>\n            |\n            <span id=\"slider-next\">\n            </span>\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <ul class=\"bxslider1 clients-list\">\n          <@cms_content catalogalias=\"business\" size=\"10\">\n            <#list DataList as content>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"${content.link}\" title=\"${content.title}\">\n                  <img src=\"${content.logo}\" alt=\"${content.title}\" style=\"width:142px;height:94px;\" />\n                </a>\n              </li>\n            </#list>\n          </@cms_content>\n        </ul>\n\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- END CLIENTS -->\n  </div>\n\n  <!--container end-->\n\n  <!--footer start-->\n  <@cms_include file=\"footer.template.html\"></@cms_include>\n  <!--small footer end-->\n\n  <!-- js placed at the end of the document so the pages load faster\n<script src=\"${Prefix}js/jquery.js\">\n</script>\n-->\n  <script src=\"${Prefix}js/jquery-1.8.3.min.js\">\n  </script>\n  <script src=\"${Prefix}js/bootstrap.min.js\">\n  </script>\n  <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"${Prefix}js/hover-dropdown.js\">\n  </script>\n  <script defer src=\"${Prefix}js/jquery.flexslider.js\">\n  </script>\n  <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"${Prefix}assets/bxslider/jquery.bxslider.js\">\n  </script>\n\n  <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"${Prefix}js/jquery.parallax-1.1.3.js\">\n  </script>\n  <script src=\"${Prefix}js/wow.min.js\">\n  </script>\n  <script src=\"${Prefix}assets/owlcarousel/owl.carousel.js\">\n  </script>\n\n  <script src=\"${Prefix}js/jquery.easing.min.js\">\n  </script>\n  <script src=\"${Prefix}js/link-hover.js\">\n  </script>\n  <script src=\"${Prefix}js/superfish.js\">\n  </script>\n  <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"${Prefix}js/parallax-slider/jquery.cslider.js\">\n  </script>\n  <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n    $(function () {\n\n      $(\'#da-slider\').cslider({\n        autoplay: true,\n        bgincrement: 100\n      });\n\n    });\n  </script>\n\n\n\n  <!--common script for all pages-->\n  <script src=\"${Prefix}js/common-scripts.js\">\n  </script>\n\n  <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n    jQuery(document).ready(function () {\n\n\n      $(\'.bxslider1\').bxSlider({\n        minSlides: 5,\n        maxSlides: 6,\n        slideWidth: 360,\n        slideMargin: 2,\n        moveSlides: 1,\n        responsive: true,\n        nextSelector: \'#slider-next\',\n        prevSelector: \'#slider-prev\',\n        nextText: \'Onward →\',\n        prevText: \'← Go back\'\n      });\n\n    });\n\n\n  </script>\n\n\n  <script>\n    $(\'a.info\').tooltip();\n\n    $(window).load(function () {\n      $(\'.flexslider\').flexslider({\n        animation: \"slide\",\n        start: function (slider) {\n          $(\'body\').removeClass(\'loading\');\n        }\n      });\n    });\n\n    $(document).ready(function () {\n\n      $(\"#owl-demo\").owlCarousel({\n\n        items: 4\n\n      });\n\n    });\n\n    jQuery(document).ready(function () {\n      jQuery(\'ul.superfish\').superfish();\n    });\n\n    new WOW().init();\n\n\n  </script>\n</body>\n\n</html>', 19049, 1684920353843, '__system', '2023-03-09 19:22:13', 'admin', '2023-05-24 17:25:54', NULL);
